        "ability details": "* Tracer's Pulse Bomb does damage when stuck to someone and when it explodes.\n* The projectile can be destroyed while in air by <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Defense Matrix\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-dva3.png|sub|link=D.Va#Defense Matrix|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[D.Va#Defense Matrix|Defense Matrix]]</span>, <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Kinetic Grasp\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Abilities-sigma3.png|sub|link=Sigma#Kinetic Grasp|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Sigma#Kinetic Grasp|Kinetic Grasp]]</span>, <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Javelin Spin\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability_JavelinSpin.png|sub|link=Orisa#Javelin Spin|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Orisa#Javelin Spin|Javelin Spin]]</span>, <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Power Matrix\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Perk_PowerMatrix.png|sub|link=Doomfist#Power Matrix|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Doomfist#Power Matrix|Power Matrix]]</span> and <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Kekkai Sanctuary\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:ULT Kekkai Sancturary.png|sub|link=Mizuki#Kekkai Sanctuary|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Mizuki#Kekkai Sanctuary|Kekkai Sanctuary]]</span> and reflected by <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Deflect\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-genji2.png|sub|link=Genji#Deflect|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Genji#Deflect|Deflect]]</span>, but a stuck bomb and the explosion are unaffected.\n* <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Amplification Matrix\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Baptiste-ability4.png|sub|link=Baptiste#Amplification Matrix|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Baptiste#Amplification Matrix|Amplification Matrix]]</span> a